{"tid":2154853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西雞翼表面樣本，對新型肺炎病毒檢測呈陽性","createTime":"2020-08-13T11:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T12:34:25.000Z","uid":25409,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"97d24912cdd7d57e7eb70169ea08b39f1e08f91e","tid":2154853,"uid":25409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"內地增19人確診 深圳有巴西雞翼表面樣本檢測呈陽性<br />\n2020-08-13 HKT 09:15<br />\n<br />\n&quot;內地過去一日新增19宗新型肺炎確診病例，新疆的本土病例有8宗，其餘11宗都由境外輸入......<br />\n<br />\n深圳龍崗1份由巴西進口的凍雞翼表面樣本，對病毒檢測呈陽性，當局對可能接觸產品的人員進行檢測，結果都是陰性，對全市相關庫存產品的檢測亦是陰性，有關部門繼續進行追溯檢測排查工作，並提醒市民購買進口冷凍肉製品和水產品時做好個人防護，降低感染風險。 &quot;<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543441-20200813.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543441-20200813.htm&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzpKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=bc39c0a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543441-20200813.htm&h=4ed8ad33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543441-20200813.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雞翼呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7574be2a1853b14024158d584e14a29f82fed0","tid":2154853,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df5fb85f3212a30e3401ac19742c93023c98c2e","tid":2154853,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a644de6a626d6c593afdc3abd4697d24d1bd3d54","tid":2154853,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}